MIME media type name : Application

MIME subtype name : Vendor Tree - vnd.canon-CPDL

Required parameters : none

Optional parameters : none

Encoding considerations : 
CPDL(Canon's PDL)files consists of the command code for
printers processed by pages.
They may additionally contain text data or binary data such as images
and should be encoded using Content-Transfer-Encoding base64.

Security considerations : 
The security considerations of this type have not been assessed.
If delivery of this type to a printer which is not able to parsing the
format of this type may result in unexpected behavior.
